USING Progress.Lang.*.

BLOCK-LEVEL ON ERROR UNDO, THROW.

CLASS Hand:
  
  DEFINE PUBLIC VARIABLE oCardsInHand AS CLASS Card EXTENT 4 NO-UNDO.

  CONSTRUCTOR PUBLIC Hand():
    DEFINE VARIABLE itx AS INTEGER NO-UNDO.

    DO itx = 1 TO 4:
      oCardsInHand[itx] = NEW Card("",0).
    END.        
  END CONSTRUCTOR.
  
  METHOD PUBLIC Card discard(INPUT ipoCard AS Card):
    DEFINE VARIABLE itx AS INTEGER NO-UNDO.

    DO itx = 1 TO 4:
      IF THIS-OBJECT:oCardsInHand[itx] = ipoCard THEN
      DO:
        ASSIGN
          THIS-OBJECT:oCardsInHand[itx]:cType  = "Empty"
          THIS-OBJECT:oCardsInHand[itx]:cName  = ""
          THIS-OBJECT:oCardsInHand[itx]:iValue = 0.        
        RETURN THIS-OBJECT:oCardsInHand[itx].
      END.
    END.        
  END.

  DESTRUCTOR PUBLIC Hand():
  END DESTRUCTOR.

END CLASS.